console-setup (1.185) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Team upload

  [ Cyril Brulebois ]
  * setupcon(findfile): Do not use `ls` in order to find a file because
    `ls` sorts its arguments.  Thanks to Alexey Shilin (patch provided),
    closes: #898303.
