  * Support XKB rules with multiple consequents (thanks, Adam Simpkins;
    LP: #139710).
  * Allow specifying alternate rules using XKBRULES (thanks, Adam Simpkins;
    LP: #139712).
  * Handle some special cases for the KPDL key (LP: #189529).

